About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • USB-C Extension Cord: Designed for extending the connection between USB-C devices such as Type-C smartphone or laptop for charging or data syncing. It can acess hard-to-reach place and protect USB Type C female port of your device from frequent plugging and unplugging, protecting console from getting scratched by the dock.
  • Fast Charging for Multi devices: UGREEN type C extension cable can reach as high as 20V/5A charging power when using a C-C 5A charging cable to charge a laptop of USB C port. For cell phones, this USB C extender could realize Power Delivery 3A fast charging without degrading the power efficiency.
  • Ultra High Speed for Transmitting: UGREEN USB C 3.1 Gen 2 extension Cable support max. 10gbps data transmitting and 3840*2160 60HZ image definition no matter for the devices with USB C port or thunderbolt port, free your anxiety and frustration from long latency time and data delay.
  • Support 4K Video and Audio Transfer: Support up to 3840*2160 60HZ 4K video signal transferring for the connection between your MacBook to another monitor or display with USB C interface. Note: Please make sure both your input laptop and output monitor type c ports support video in and out function(Thunderbolt 3).
  • Extensive Compatibility: USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type C extension cable can be compatible with Nintendo Switch, iMac Pro, Google Nexus 5X 6P, Pixel 2 2 XL, Pixel Pixel XL, Pixel C, Microsoft Lumia 950 950XL, Samsung Galaxy S8 S8 Plus, Apple MacBook 2017 2016 12 inch, MacBook Pro 13" 2016 2017, Google Chromebook Pixel, Huawei Matebook, Dell XPS 13 15, LG G7 ThinQ V30 V20 G5 G6 etc.

Product Description

Read more

Extend without Decreasing Power Delivery Ability:

As a type C extension cable, UGREEN make it to support max. 20V/5A charging power, when you use it to charge your laptop or cell phone, UGREEN usb c extension cable can adjust the power automatically by its internal chip and realize the charging effects of original device in biggest degree. So it is very practical to regard this usb c extender as a admirable backup for the original charging cable.

Unforgettable Vision and Audio Experience:

UGREEN type c 3.1 Gen 2 extension cable can sync the data transmission in 10gbps speed and support 4K@60HZ UHD resolution, so it is a very proper partner to balance the data transmission and the image definition during gaming play, video watching, meeting, PPT presentation. In a word , thanks to UGREEN usb c extension cable although the storage base is different, the enjoyment brought by this cable is simultaneous.

Broad Compatibility:

Compatible for Nintendo Switch, MacBook 2016, 2017, USB-C Apple Digital AV Multiport Adapter

Compatible for Samsung Galaxy Note 8, S8, S8 Plus, LG G6, G5, V30, V20, Samsung Dex Dock, Nexus 5X, 6P

Compatible for Google Chrombook Pixel, Dell XPS 13 15,Inspiron 5000,Inspiron 7000, Lenovo ThinkPad X270, HP Envy x360,Pavilion x360,Spectre x360

Note:

1. The QD fast charging will come true only when the device support QD protocol.

2. The 3840*2160 can only works when the output/input devices support 4K.

3. For the best performance, pls use this USB C extension cable with 2 meters.

Read more
Read more

One Cable, One World:

UGREEN USB C 3.1 Gen 2 extension Cable support max. 10gbps data transmitting and 3840*2160 60HZ image definition no matter for the devices with USB C port or thunderbolt port, not only lower down the latency greatly but also combine the different data world into one world.

Smart Chip for smart use:

New upgraded internal chip ensures safe connection, and by virtue of special algorithm this usb c extension cable can fit almost all of the usb c devices and adjust the power rate intelligently, realeasing you from the trouble of compatibility.

Fast charging, not only for fast:

During charging process, safety, fast, and stability are the only goal; UGREEN male to female usb c cable can support 5V/3A 9V/2A 9V/3A 12V/3A 15V/3A 20V/3A and 20V/5A, each power setting is prepared to satisfy your charging needs.

      5.0 out of 5 stars Great cable - Know your limits on TBT3
      Reviewed in the United States on March 30, 2018
      Size: 1.5FTVerified Purchase
      Theres seriously too much disinformation and confusion floating around the reviews for TBT3 (Thunderbolt 3) devices. I honestly dont think that the general public knows the potential of TBT3, yet, or more people would be all about it.

      For my part:

      This 1.5ft USB-C TBT3 extension cable worked exactly as-intended to extend a Tikko-brand generic USB-C TBT3 hub for my laptops workstation setup at the office. Thank god for the extra 18 inches (never said that one before).

      My intended use-case was to extend aforementioned hub, which only came with a ~1ft Thunderbolt 3 connector built into the side of it - which left me with having to either place the hub in eyeshot on my workstation (and all cables going into the hub along with it) or to extend the TBT3 cable (and hide the hub from eyeshot, leaving just have this cable sticking out, ready to plug-in). This extension worked excellently for the latter.

      Charging worked great as well - havent tested if the fast-charge worked over this extension cable but I could test if anyone needed to know badly enough ahead of time.
